{"tid":152702,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過聽 effortless English?","createTime":"2017-03-12T04:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T15:27:48.000Z","uid":17542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1452a8195a6fb6082ac1dafa7c404c2851cc2b7","tid":152702,"uid":17542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"覺得有無用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e905d808f212ac09aaebfa91bb0013b1f99f4f","tid":152702,"uid":17542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d93b1c64f48fcc5e170abb52c6a909980930d02","tid":152702,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得睇youtube好過，有畫面差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55076412602d2a96c406a65c15925a650a446d98","tid":152702,"uid":17542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得睇youtube好過，有畫面差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係好悶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6112f8741a36c28393a616addf6c0c8dfdcb8805","tid":152702,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得睇youtube好過，有畫面差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係好悶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係悶唔悶問題，係有畫面容易入腦，例如睇drama會記得成個故事，講野個語氣，咩時候用咩野講法等等"},{"pid":"7528b6afb15959106e2ea7fb8ce098dc5b9353e9","tid":152702,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"聽過幾集 自己懶 之後無聽<br />\nenglishpod 聽過幾十集 聽力係好左小小"},{"pid":"0f8d5b5681744085be8384378dbf0eb83c4aa7d0","tid":152702,"uid":17542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得睇youtube好過，有畫面差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係好悶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係悶唔悶問題，係有畫面容易入腦，例如睇drama會記得成個故事，講野個語氣，咩時候用咩野講法等等</blockquote><br />\n佢嗰隻係要你洗腦式咁聽十幾次"},{"pid":"1ae94bc0ccdc204b65439137d258a7a3fea7efbd","tid":152702,"uid":33618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得睇youtube好過，有畫面差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係好悶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係悶唔悶問題，係有畫面容易入腦，例如睇drama會記得成個故事，講野個語氣，咩時候用咩野講法等等</blockquote><br />\n佢嗰隻係要你洗腦式咁聽十幾次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔淨只佢果隻，你學咩語言都係，睇youtube又好，聽錄音又好，都係重複又重複，重複又重複，一定要有大量input，十幾次係太少，起碼要過百次<br />\n你可以搵條youtube短片，大約半個鐘，不斷loop，可以過埋落手機，轉埋mp3，日日狂煲，我以家就係咁做緊<br />\n介紹埋兩個app俾你，一個chrom app，叫Looper for youtube，可以set時間不斷loop一句或一段<br />\n另一個係android app，叫EarFlip，又係可以set looping，仲可以較播放速度<br />\nBTW，加油爸打"},{"pid":"9242f7fc4039dc26965f863331be3b464d524e4a","tid":152702,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47e5cae16824318e2afddaf610471755622d3d3b","tid":152702,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T13:46:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b089682e46c1651c69daacb34a604b4064595d7","tid":152702,"uid":27129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"我都試過不斷聽同一段日文 但最後因為太悶放棄咗<br />\n聆聽係學語言最重要一環 但實際練習嘅時候真係好難堅持"},{"pid":"457f0c0e13a4ce971cbbea4bee12c07bdbe6e67d","tid":152702,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:12:34.000Z","msg":"有佢成個course file <br />\n淘寶有得買"},{"pid":"a615cfacf7c45d36823f0450f32fb4c6aad700ae","tid":152702,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得睇youtube好過，有畫面差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係好悶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係悶唔悶問題，係有畫面容易入腦，例如睇drama會記得成個故事，講野個語氣，咩時候用咩野講法等等</blockquote><br />\n唔關事..係有啲人有視覺去配合, 有啲人係聽覺為主<br />\n其實冇絕對囉..<br />\n我唔鍾意睇電視, 鍾意聽廣播劇嘅..<br />\n唔通我又想像唔到個畫面咩..兼夾訓練聯想力<br />\n反而仲可以集中啲去訓練聆聽, 唔會有哂hints 去畀你估..<br />\n唔通盲人就學唔得好語言咩..??<br />\n<br />\n每個人學習方式都唔同, <br />\n況且effortless eng 係一個耳濡目染咁製造個環境到畀你去適應<br />\n佢係不斷重覆問你同一條問題, 要你去答, 可以問完唔同題目再返兜<br />\n其實以前靈格風類似...<br />\n目的係等你可以好快好自然咁去用該語言回應<br />\n係密集式去訓練你嘅潛意識, 唔使等你反應對答時要左頹右諗去用大腦去翻譯<br />\n有個program 好多嘅心理學, 神經學嘅理論喺背後支持<br />\n其他外語嘅聆聽錄音都有類似嘅方式..<br />\n所以係唔需要畫面..因為目的並唔係要令你吸收好多嘅詞彙<br />\n<br />\n至於咩睇drama..其實只係被動吸收上嘅途徑..<br />\neffortless 係幫助啲人去適應個語境..訓練輸出時嘅思維<br />\n到你用到咁上下時..你習慣咗..就用諗得好咗順咗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nvideo conferencing 定 phone conferencing ，邊樣會溝通得好D？<br />\n以家係學英文，唔係訓練聯想力，OK？<br />\n程度唔夠走去聽廣播劇，想像唔到個畫面有幾奇？<br />\n盲人都可以學得好語言，但同健全人比，邊個學得快D？"},{"pid":"813f76d8b8e2c46293f84dca8b5c9e2ca773b079","tid":152702,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有佢成個course file <br />\n淘寶有得買</blockquote><br />\n如果小小錢都唔想比 上網係有得down (大約半年前仲有link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e7e09f47c803bb222e4873cf0069a8042bd357","tid":152702,"uid":44016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有佢成個course file <br />\n淘寶有得買</blockquote><br />\n如果小小錢都唔想比 上網係有得down (大約半年前仲有link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42365c15b71760606e1aa38a3687ac00b2d260b","tid":152702,"uid":17542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s